# Optional: GitHub personal access token for higher API rate limits and contribution data.
# Without it: 60 req/hr for REST; no contribution calendar on About page.
# Create at https://github.com/settings/tokens — enable "read:user" for contribution calendar.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Optional: Upstash Redis for persistent visitor counter in the footer.
# Without it: counter uses in-memory storage and resets on serverless cold start.
# Create at https://upstash.com — then add REST URL and token.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
